The inter-team effectiveness survey consists of 10 questions intended to measure feedback around themes such as collaboration, conflict management, communication, transparency, etc among various teams in the organization. Your feedback will help us in improving the manner in which teams work with each other and leverage synergies effectively

The teams listed in the survey are customized based on the function you are a part of. Your feedback should be based on your working experience with these teams.

children.title: Form

children.text: Use the form below to fill additional Input
Incase, there is any other team for which you want to share the feedback, please select the button "Click for Additional Feedback" , Else select the "Submit" button .
PS : For the best experience, please take this survey from your laptop/ PC

Survey Instructions:

1) Please note the survey has 10 questions and you can answer each of them by navigating at the scroll bar at the bottom. You can also adjust the horizontal scroll bar to navigate through all the streams 
2) Please click on the pen symbol to bring the drop down and record your inputs
3) Once you have completed the inputs for one stream/ department, please click on the "Save" button to record your inputs and move to the next row 
4) If there is any department/ team which is not relevant (due to nature/ extent of interactions not being significant enough), please mark the "Is The Team Relevant?" question as "No" and proceed to the next row
5) If you want to provide any qualitative feedback to the teams mentioned in the list, use the "Tell Us More" option in the last column
6) If you want to provide feedback to any team not present in the list, please use the "Click for Additional" option
7) Once you have completed the survey, please click on Submit button at the end to close the record your inputs
